critique: This document adjusts trade preferences under the Generalized System of Preferences (GSP). It removes item 706.39 from the list of eligible articles for GSP benefits and modifies general headnote 3(c)(iii) of the TSUS by deleting item number 706.39 for Hong Kong, Republic of Korea, and Taiwan. The changes are effective retroactively to January 1, 1976, for articles imported on or after that date and entered/withdrawn from warehouse on or after June 25, 1984.
